rows.label: qst201103_0010
rows.name:
The note said for us to look somewhere
around here...

rows.label: qst201103_0020
rows.name: Not a single soul in sight...

rows.label: qst201103_0030
rows.name:
Any chance someone was pulling a fast
one on us?

rows.label: qst201103_0050
rows.name:
I doubt it. 'Cos really, who'd go this far
to play tricks on us?

rows.label: qst201103_0090
rows.name:
I'm fine. It seems they never intended
to actually hit us.

rows.label: qst201103_0100
rows.name: Again with the lance? I really don't get this.

rows.label: qst201103_0130
rows.name: Let's go after them! Uhh...or not.

rows.label: qst201103_0140
rows.name:
Indeed. I don't believe we'd be able
to catch up.

rows.label: qst201103_0150
rows.name:
But never mind that. Is there something
written on this lance too?
